        <item>
            <title>Lets Mute 1.1.2.6b14</title>
            <pubDate>Mon, 26 May 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
            <sparkle:version>14</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.1.2.6b14</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>14.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <description><![CDATA[
                <h3>What's new in 1.1.2.6b14</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>Fixed the Input Monitoring permission dialog appearing on launch when Accessibility permission had been revoked (e.g. after re-installing from a DMG)</li>
                    <li>Hotkey engine now silently waits for Input Monitoring to be granted rather than triggering the system dialog unexpectedly</li>
                </ul>
            ]]></description>
